share prices rose in early trading on the london stock exchange today, continuing the market's recent upswing
the financial times-stock exchange 100 index was little changed when the market officially opened at 9 a.m. up 0.1 points at 1,813.4
but it started rising immediately and at 9:45 a.m., the index was up 7.8 points at 1,821.1
