a frontal system off the pacific coast brought scattered rainshowers along the coast of oregon and northwest california
for today, snow was forecast from northern and western pennsylvania across new york and new england; scattered rain or snow across southeast missouri, southern illinois, and northern sections of the ohio valley; rain from kentucky and tennessee through the middle atlantic coast region, with showers and thunderstorms likely over northern florida, alabama, georgia and the carolinas; scattered rain or snow showers across the northern high plains; snowshowers widely scattered over the mountains of wyoming and colorado; and rain across the pacific northwest
