four weeks ended feb. 27: $699.1 million, up 16.2 percent from $601.8 million
four weeks ended feb. 27: $598.2 million, down 1.3 percent from $606 million
four weeks ended feb. 27: $269.6 million, down 2.5 percent from $276.7 million
